#############################################

Start/Restart production environment:

# start god (monitoring server)


# re/start Resque 
god restart resque

# (re)start ortodontics360 (placed in /etc/init/)
# see also http://blog.daviddollar.org/2011/05/06/introducing-foreman.html
sudo (re)start orthodontics360 

# start Sphinx server

1. start/restart server:
RAILS_ROOT="." RAILS_ENV=production god -c resque.god
god restart resque
sudo restart orthodontics360 (restart Foreman's script aded to upstream http://blog.daviddollar.org/2011/05/06/introducing-foreman.html)
RAILS_ENV=production rake ts:run (launches Sphinx)
whenever (refreshes cron's task list)

2 start/restart env
  RAILS_ENV=production rake assets:clean &&  rake assets:precompile && god restart resque && sudo restart orthodontics360





